9. Fidelity Tiering

To manage computational cost, the NSB operates under attention-based fidelity tiers.

Tier	Scope	Representation
Tier 1	distant world	symbolic geometry
Tier 2	interactive region	full spatial runtime
Tier 3	focal region	neural high-fidelity rendering

This aligns compute resources with user attention.

