10. Evaluation Metrics

The NSB can be evaluated using the following criteria:
	•	Identity continuity
Objects remain referenceable across time.
	•	Affordance fidelity
Objects behave according to intended purpose.
	•	Spatial coherence
Objects integrate with the environment.
	•	Perceptual plausibility
Rendered output appears coherent.
	•	Translation invariant retention
Core meaning survives across representations.

